overview: April can't help crushing on her dad's partner, Rocco. So when he comes by for some work, she'll offer him a whole new kind of work out.  Dana is a concerned teacher who only wants the best for her student, Johnny, even if it means extra lessons in his bedroom.  The family antics spread to the friends of the kids, as Jessie and Chris take advantage of the house for some filthy fun.  The kids think their dad, Charles, is uptight. They bring him an even tighter piece of ass to help him unwind.  Mom needs a bit of release too, so the kids bring her the gardener to rake her turf and spill some seeds
title: Filthy Family 5
